{"tid":1894750,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"波蘭 CD Projekt 成為歐洲僅次育碧的第二大遊戲開發商","createTime":"2020-02-24T06:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T22:11:08.000Z","uid":33359,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"661a9fb2a18223075e2b5b05eeac6e1d46ff2adc","tid":1894750,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:19:24.000Z","msg":"波蘭 CD Projekt 成為歐洲僅次育碧的第二大遊戲開發商<br />\n<a href=\"https://times.hinet.net/mobile/topic/22795142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimes.hinet.net%2Fmobile%2Ftopic%2F22795142&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=eea15408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://times.hinet.net/mobile/topic/22795142</a><br />\n<br />\n人氣年度遊戲《巫師3》開發商 CD Projekt 近日有新的里程碑，根據最新資訊，該公司<br />\n市值已超過 315.2 億波蘭茲羅提（約為 79.5 億美元），也就是成為歐洲僅次於育碧的<br />\n第二大遊戲開發商。<br />\n<br />\n《巫師3》上市以來，CD Projekt 就被廣大玩家以「佛心」形容，不僅僅是因為作品相當<br />\n優秀，價格方面也總是讓玩家覺得很超值。近期 Netflix 上獨佔的《巫師》影集，《巫<br />\n師 3》登上 Switch，再加上預計於今年 9 月 17 日上市的最新作品 《電馭叛客 2077》<br />\n，這些舉動也都使 CD Projekt 吸引到更多的資金。<br />\n<br />\n雖然市值離育碧還有一段距離，但也許《電馭叛客 2077》上市，或者是曾表示將開發的<br />\n《巫師》系列遊戲，這些超「吸金」的作品加上公司良好的形象也許能讓 CD Projekt 的<br />\n市值超越育碧也說不定。"},{"pid":"3e9a4cf7ad96bcb05d109e226d04d1977f7393b4","tid":1894750,"uid":111460,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://external-preview.redd.it/DT0II-IFQqyf1KvLlkRygxXNHgKaYTx4YnK592o_XWQ.jpg?auto=webp&amp;s=0cc12821586ab09a95baf39d0e6e5098d51df15e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal-preview.redd.it%2FDT0II-IFQqyf1KvLlkRygxXNHgKaYTx4YnK592o_XWQ.jpg%3Fauto%3Dwebp%26s%3D0cc12821586ab09a95baf39d0e6e5098d51df15e&h=32054c58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71f128ae4eaebd306d93ca158bd4a1d729054f14","tid":1894750,"uid":267328,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"3e9a4cf7ad96bcb05d109e226d04d1977f7393b4","tid":1894750,"uid":111460,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2